  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to monitor the safety and efficacy of CUBICIN under conditions
      of actual use in patients who are diagnosed with complicated Skin and Skin Structure
      infection (cSSI) or Staphylococcus aureus bacteria including right-sided endocarditis and are
      prescribed CUBICIN by their physician.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
